data.description:
Enjoy this all stucco and stone home with five bedrooms, three full baths, a spacious kitchen with island, vaulted ceilings, walk-out basement, deck, and main floor laundry room. Located on the southern border of Smithfield, this home has beautiful views of scenic Cache Valley as well as mountain views. This well-kept home is very cozy and livable inside and out--with a beautifully landscaped yard featuring mature trees and shrubs. Sq ft per tax data. 
Call 801-244-7906
data.whatILove: It has been one of homiest home I've ever lived in.  I hate to have to leave it.  The neighborhood is amazing and it's in a great location!
